 * SPEC-01 reference snippet — Cisco TunnelGroupName in RADIUS Access-Request
 *
 * Integrate into src/auth/radius.c (ocserv 1.2.x) if unified patch does not apply.
 * Requires dictionary.vpnplatform (PW_TUNNELGROUPNAME / VSA 146) in radcli dictionary.
 */

